title: Train Simulator 2018
description: The Ultimate Rail HobbyTrain Simulator fully immerses you in a World of trains, transporting you to a place where you decide what to do, where and when.  Experience the challenge of mastering a wide variety of different locos and learning the routes in every direction.  Unlock your creative potential using powerful tools to create your very own routes and scenarios and enjoy your collection from the perspective of the driver, passenger or railfan.  Whatever you love about trains, Train
